1
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,600
Aqin

2
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:27,760
Aqin

3
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,200
Yu Tong

4
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:56,160
I finally found you.

5
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:58,240
I thought you had left.

6
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,760
How could you leave without saying goodbye?

7
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,160
You are still leaving.

8
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,400
Mr. Yuwen.

9
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,040
I'm sorry.

10
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,520
After you left yesterday,

11
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:13,480
I thought about it all night.

12
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,560
I have decided.

13
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:18,040
I must go back and marry Ao Tian.

14
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,800
You should just forget about me.

15
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,800
Why?

16
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,880
Didn't we agree

17
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,080
to face this together?

18
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:27,040
Just treat it

19
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,880
as a dream.

20
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,640
You're lying to me, aren't you?

21
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:37,720
You know that Ao Tian is no good.

22
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:40,200
Ao Tian's father holds real power.

23
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,720
He has been pushing for war against Wei.

24
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:44,440
That's why there are so many spies

25
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,520
coming to Wei Kingdom.

26
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,000
So only if I go back

27
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,200
and marry him,

28
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:49,880
is it possible

29
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:52,080
to persuade my father and ministers to stop the war.

30
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,880
Otherwise, Daye Kingdom will surely attack.

31
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,920
Such a huge burden,

32
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,320
why must you, a woman, bear it alone?

33
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,880
You are the Strategist of Wei.

34
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,360
Resourceful and wise,

35
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,640
famous throughout the world.

36
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,840
Do you have any other way?

37
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:16,720
How can there be so many perfect endings in this world?

38
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,760
To have had the honor of walking this path with you, Sir,

39
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,960
I have no regrets in this life.

40
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,200
For Wei to have subjects like you

41
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,840
is a blessing for the people.

42
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,240
What is the point of war anyway?

43
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,200
But...

44
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,600
No buts.

45
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,240
My mind is made up.

46
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,240
Your Highness is righteous.

47
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,200
For Daye Kingdom to have a princess like you

48
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,480
is the people's good fortune,

49
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,040
a blessing for the commoners.

50
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,040
Rest assured.

51
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,040
As long as Daye does not use force,

52
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,120
I can ensure both countries

53
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,640
remain at peace forever.

54
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,160
Mr. Yuwen,

55
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,680
is there anything else?

56
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:15,880
Well, this...

57
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,480
I never expected you to leave,

58
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,080
so I wasn't prepared.

59
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,760
Here is a gift for you.

60
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,200
It's the thought that counts.

61
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,240
You asked me to come here,

62
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,360
just to stand around?

63
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:47,520
No, no.

64
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,560
What I mean is,

65
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,920
I drank too much last night.

66
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,640
I might have said some things I shouldn't have.

67
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,840
Please forgive me.

68
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,680
General Wei.

69
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,600
Code of the martial world.

70
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,320
Let's have a fight.

71
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,000
If you win, I'll listen to you.

72
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,080
If you lose, you listen to me.

73
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,240
No need to fight.

74
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,160
I'll listen to you regardless.

75
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,200
Besides,

76
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,680
I can't beat you anyway.

77
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,680
Fine.

78
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,040
Then listen to me.

79
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,320
I...

80
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:30,960
You should leave.

81
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,760
What did you say?

82
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,520
I said,

83
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:37,800
you should leave.

84
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,600
It was because of a marriage contract

85
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,880
that you came to my side.

86
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,640
This made me mistakenly think you liked me.

87
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,880
When I started liking you,

88
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,840
I realized that wasn't the case.

89
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,200
A girl like you

90
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:55,040
shouldn't be bound by a piece of paper.

91
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,080
The outside world

92
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,320
is waiting for you to explore.

93
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,560
So,

94
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,240
you should go.

95
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,480
Wei Long.

96
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,520
You are a good man.

97
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,680
At a time like this,

98
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,520
why say such things?

99
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,320
Let's meet again in the martial world.

100
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,400
See you in the martial world.

101
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,080
She even gave me a "nice guy" card.

102
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,720
I'm free.

103
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:09,720
Let's go.

104
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:10,680
Let's go.

105
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,920
Let's think on the way back.

106
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,400
How do we tell the Lord?

107
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,400
About something this big.

108
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,640
We can only tell the truth.

109
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,400
Tell the truth.

110
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:21,800
Alright then.

111
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,520
Just say the Lord bestowed wine,

112
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,560
and Wei Qiao got drunk.

113
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:25,720
Wei Qiao went to Treasure Pavilion,

114
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,680
and smashed a vat.

115
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,600
On the way out to fix the vat,

116
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,720
he even crippled someone.

117
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,320
When we got to the village,

118
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,160
he even... that little girl...

119
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,120
No way, brother.

120
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,320
We can't say that.

121
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,280
Why can't we say that?

122
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,320
Wei Long.

123
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,840
Did he really... with Xiao Hua?

124
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:36,720
Don't.

125
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,320
I saw it that day.

126
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,440
Where's the carriage?

127
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,760
Gentlemen.

128
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:52,720
How is it?

129
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,200
This thing I recommended to the Lord...

130
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:56,200
The crayfish economic policy isn't bad, right?

131
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:56,960
Look.

132
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,040
This place has become a famous

133
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,440
tourist attraction.

134
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:02,040
I haven't eaten crayfish here in a long time.

135
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,640
Once we arrive,

136
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,520
we'll have a good meal.

137
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,200
Strategist.

138
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,200
Have you heard?

139
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,560
Half a year ago,

140
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,720
Daye Kingdom's Princess Consort was arrested for corruption.

141
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,680
The Third Princess

142
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,000
even divorced him.

143
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,080
He wasn't a good person anyway.

144
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,160
Not surprising.

145
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,120
But what is strange is,

146
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,880
ever since that incident,

147
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,800
the Third Princess

148
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,200
has never appeared again.

149
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,360
Is that strange?

150
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,320
Not strange.

151
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,000
Boss Lady.

152
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,800
Do you still need a boss here?
